### 5.4 [citation_pruner.py](file:///Users/arshadshaik/Desktop/ArshadForge/agents/citation_pruner.py) (56 lines)

**Purpose**: Deterministic scoring to remove irrelevant vector citations.

#### Scoring Scheme

| Condition | Score |
|---|---|
| Citation contains exact answer value | +3 |
| Citation contains anchor phrase (e.g., "employment") | +2 |
| Citation page matches validated page exactly | +2 |
| Citation page is ┬▒1 from validated page | +1 |
| Citation does NOT contain answer value | тИТ2 |

**Minimum score to keep**: 2

This prevents noisy vector results from polluting the final response.

