| 3 | Forecasting (CAGR) | "What is the required CAGR to hit the 2030 target?" | CAGR тЙИ 10.00% (┬▒2%), contains baseline 7351, target 17333, formula |
| 4 | Arithmetic | "What is 17333 divided by 7351?" | Uses calculator, contains both numbers |

Each test returns a structured dict with `passed`, `checks`, `raw_answer`, `tools_used`, and `trace_id`. Results are saved to `logs/test_summary.json`.

The harness also checks for **strict SQL mode** from the health endpoint and adds an additional assertion (`strict_single_source`) if enabled.

