## 10. Weaknesses & Improvement Opportunities

| Area | Issue | Suggestion |
|---|---|---|
| **Security** | `eval()` in calculator tool is not truly sandboxed | Use `ast.literal_eval` or subprocess sandbox |
| **Security** | No API authentication | Add API key or OAuth middleware |
| **Security** | CORS is fully open | Restrict to known origins |
| **Scalability** | SQLite is single-writer | Migrate to PostgreSQL |
| **Scalability** | ChromaDB is local-only | Migrate to PGVector or Pinecone |
| **Scalability** | Single-document design | Add document_id to all tables, collection sharding |
| **Hardcoded data** | Seed data requires manual curation per report | Automate more table parsing with validation |
| **Table parsing** | pdfplumber fails on merged cells, rotated text | Add OCR+layout analysis fallback |
| **LLM** | llama3:8b limits answer quality for general queries | Upgrade to larger model or API |
| **README** | Duplicate numbered items (3, 4 repeated in "How Factual Reliability") | Minor editorial fix needed |
| **Testing** | Tests run against live API only | Add unit tests for individual tools and planner |
| **Error handling** | Some `except Exception` catches are too broad | Catch specific exceptions |

